  			User 
----------------------------------------------
user schema
_id,name,surname,designation,email,phone,role,branch,register_date,point,orderCount,
total_order,Nationality,Birthdate



 1. For user registration
 method-->POST
 URL--->http://localhost:5000/api/users/register
 body-->{
    "designation":"MR",
  "name": "demo",
  "surname": "demo",
  "email": "demo@gmail.com",
  "phone":"+919988776655",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456",
  "role": "online_customer",
    "nationality":"India"
}

for online customer need password 
for super market customer no need password --offline shopping 




2.Login
Method-->POST
URL-->http://localhost:5000/api/users/login
body-->{
    "email": "vinay@gmail.com",
    "password": "vinay@123"
}




3.refresh-token
Method-->POST
URL-->http://localhost:5000/api/users/refresh-token
body-->empty




4.Password change manually
Method-->POST
URL-->http://localhost:5000/api/users/change-password
body-->{ "userId":"test@gmail.com",
    "oldPassword": "123456", "newPassword": "1234567" }




5.Reset Password
Method-->POST
URL-->http://localhost:5000/api/users/forgot-password
body-->{
    "email": "test@gmail.com"
}

it give you a reset link look like--{
    "message": "Password reset link sent",
    "resetUrl": "http://localhost:5000/api/users/reset/4d813a8dac8e7a6cad95584ec5848413a76ddddcdd94ab64b9d3505ba2f03c88"
}

valid for 15 min

click on link then in body send 
{"password":"123456"}

all working done by post request




6.Get all user data
Method-->GET
URL-->http://localhost:5000/api/users/getdata
params-->empty




7.fetch user detail specific
Method-->GET
URL-->http://localhost:5000/api/users/getdata?email=test@gmail.com
params-->email:test@gmail.com,_id:3



8.Update user data
Method-->PATCH
URL-->http://localhost:5000/api/users/updateUser
body-->
{
  "condition_obj": {
    "email": "test@gmail.com"
  },
  "content_obj": {
    "name": "testing"
  }
}



9.fetch user data using phone number ----only user role==supermarket_customer, online_customer
Method-->GET
URL-->http://localhost:5000/api/users/get-customer/0987654321
params-->emty



10.delete user
Method-->DELETE
URL-->http://localhost:5000/api/users/delete
body-->{
  "email": "test22@gmail.com"
}


