1.create brand 
METHOD->POST
URL->http://localhost:5000/api/brand
BODY->{
  "brandName": "Samsung",
  "isInList": true,
  "image": "https://i.pinimg.com/1200x/00/cc/1b/00cc1b2d9e3d0b247b2a389abaaedb37.jpg"
}



-------------------------no auth access by all 
2.fetch all brand 
METHOD->GET
URL->http://localhost:5000/api/brand
params->empty



3.Update brand 
METHOD->PUT
URL->http://localhost:5000/api/brand/1
BODY->{
  "brandName": "Samsung phone",
  "isInList": true,
  "image": "https://i.pinimg.com/1200x/00/cc/1b/00cc1b2d9e3d0b247b2a389abaaedb37.jpg"
}



4.delete brand 
METHOD->DELETE
URL->http://localhost:5000/api/brand/1



